---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Tips for Choosing the Right Family Dental Clinic | Wildwood Dental Clinic Blog"
  description="Selecting a dentist for your entire family can be challenging. Here are key things to look for when choosing a family dental clinic that meets everyone's needs."
>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="bg-[var(--color-brand-primary)] relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="hidden lg:block absolute right-0 top-0 bottom-0 w-[42%] pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true">
      <img
        src="/images/services/clinic-patient.jpg"
        alt=""
        width="800"
        height="600"
        loading="eager"
        decoding="async"
        class="w-full h-full object-cover"
      />
      <div class="absolute inset-y-0 left-0 w-2/3" style="background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--color-brand-primary), transparent);"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="container-wide relative py-16 lg:py-24 lg:max-w-[64%]">
      <nav class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-[var(--color-text-on-dark-muted)] mb-5" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
        <a href="/" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Home</a>
        <span aria-hidden="true">›</span>
        <a href="/blog" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Blog</a>
        <span aria-hidden="true">›</span>
        <span class="text-white">Choosing a Family Dental Clinic</span>
      </nav>
      <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold bg-[#dbeafe] text-[#1e40af] mb-4">Family Dentistry</span>
      <h1 class="mt-2 font-display font-semibold text-[length:var(--text-5xl)] leading-tight text-white max-w-2xl">
        Tips for Choosing the Right Family Dental Clinic
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-[var(--color-text-on-dark-muted)]">
        <time datetime="2018-08-28">August 28, 2018</time>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ARTICLE CONTENT -->
  <section class="section-y bg-white">
    <div class="container-wide">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-[1fr_300px] gap-12">

        <!-- Article body -->
        <article class="prose-content space-y-8 text-[var(--color-text)] leading-relaxed">

          <p class="text-lg text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">
            Selecting a dentist for the entire family can be challenging. After all, you want a provider who can meet the needs of adults and children alike, as well as someone who will be there for you as your family grows.
          </p>

          <div>
            <h2 class="font-display font-semibold text-[length:var(--text-3xl)] text-[var(--color-brand-primary)] mb-4">Ask for referrals</h2>
            <p>
              One of the best ways to find a quality family dental clinic is to ask for recommendations from friends, family, or colleagues. Word-of-mouth referrals from people you trust can point you toward dentists who have already earned the confidence of people in your community.
            </p>
            <p class="mt-3">
              If you are new to an area, online searches and patient reviews can help you narrow down your options. Look for consistent feedback about the quality of care, communication, and the clinic's approach to patients of all ages.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="font-display font-semibold text-[length:var(--text-3xl)] text-[var(--color-brand-primary)] mb-4">Know the dentist's areas of expertise</h2>
            <p>
              Before contacting a dental practice, consider any specialty services your family might need. Different offices offer different treatments, so it is worth confirming that a clinic can provide the procedures that matter most to you — whether that is periodontal care, pediatric dentistry, orthodontic consultations, or other services.
            </p>
            <p class="mt-3">
              A family dental clinic with a broad scope of services can reduce the need for referrals and make it easier to coordinate care for everyone in the household under one roof.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="font-display font-semibold text-[length:var(--text-3xl)] text-[var(--color-brand-primary)] mb-4">Find out if the dental office is kid-friendly</h2>
            <p>
              Early oral health experiences shape how children feel about dental care for the rest of their lives. A family dental clinic that takes time to explain procedures in a way children can understand, and that creates a welcoming environment, can make a meaningful difference in helping young patients develop healthy habits.
            </p>
            <p class="mt-3">
              When evaluating clinics, pay attention to how the staff interacts with children, and whether the environment feels calm and approachable rather than clinical and intimidating.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="font-display font-semibold text-[length:var(--text-3xl)] text-[var(--color-brand-primary)] mb-4">Things to look for when choosing a family dental clinic</h2>

            <div class="space-y-5 mt-4">
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-[var(--color-brand-primary)] text-base">Education and experience</h3>
                <p class="mt-1.5">Research the dentist's training and how long they have been in practice. Do not hesitate to ask about their experience with specific procedures that are relevant to your family's needs.</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-[var(--color-brand-primary)] text-base">Comfort level</h3>
                <p class="mt-1.5">Beyond credentials, you should feel heard, valued, and respected at every visit. A dentist who listens to your concerns and explains your options clearly helps build the kind of long-term relationship that supports good oral health.</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-[var(--color-brand-primary)] text-base">Availability</h3>
                <p class="mt-1.5">Being able to schedule an appointment within a reasonable timeframe — typically two to three weeks for a routine visit — is a sign that a practice is well-organized and can accommodate your family's schedule.</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-[var(--color-brand-primary)] text-base">Office hours and location</h3>
                <p class="mt-1.5">A clinic that is close to home or work, and offers hours that work with your schedule, makes it easier to keep up with regular appointments for every member of the family.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="border-t border-[var(--color-border-soft)] pt-8">
            <p>
              At Wildwood Dental Clinic, we welcome patients of all ages and work to make every visit a positive experience. If you have questions about whether our clinic is the right fit for your family, we would be happy to talk with you.
            </p>
            <p class="mt-3">
              Call us at <a href="tel:+13063747272" class="font-semibold text-[var(--color-brand-accent)] hover:text-[var(--color-brand-accent-hover)] transition-colors">306.374.7272</a> or use our online booking form.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="mt-4">
            <a href="/blog" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-semibold text-[var(--color-brand-primary)] hover:text-[var(--color-brand-accent)] transition-colors">
              <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><line x1="19" y1="12" x2="5" y2="12"/><polyline points="12 19 5 12 12 5"/></svg>
              Back to Blog
            </a>
          </div>

        </article>

        <!-- Sidebar -->
        <aside class="space-y-6">
          <div class="bg-[var(--color-brand-primary)] rounded-2xl p-6 text-white">
            <h3 class="font-display font-semibold text-lg mb-3">Ready to visit us?</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-on-dark-muted)] leading-relaxed mb-5">
              We welcome new patients of all ages. Book an appointment online or give us a call.
            </p>
            <a href="/book" class="btn btn-accent w-full text-center block">
              Request Appointment
            </a>
            <a href="tel:+13063747272" class="mt-3 block text-center text-sm text-[var(--color-text-on-dark-muted)] hover:text-white transition-colors">
              306.374.7272
            </a>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-[var(--color-surface-cool)] rounded-2xl p-6">
            <h3 class="font-display font-semibold text-base text-[var(--color-brand-primary)] mb-4">More Articles</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-4">
              <li>
                <a href="/blog/what-to-expect-at-your-teeth-cleaning" class="group">
                  <span class="text-xs text-[var(--color-text-muted)] block mb-1">Preventive Care</span>
                  <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-[var(--color-brand-primary)] group-hover:text-[var(--color-brand-accent)] transition-colors leading-snug block">What to Expect at Your Teeth Cleaning</span>
                </a>
              </li>
              <li>
                <a href="/blog/why-restore-a-broken-tooth" class="group">
                  <span class="text-xs text-[var(--color-text-muted)] block mb-1">Restorative Dentistry</span>
                  <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-[var(--color-brand-primary)] group-hover:text-[var(--color-brand-accent)] transition-colors leading-snug block">Why Restore a Broken Tooth?</span>
                </a>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </aside>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="section-y bg-[var(--color-surface-alt)]">
    <div class="container-wide text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="font-display font-semibold text-[length:var(--text-4xl)] leading-tight text-[var(--color-brand-primary)]">
        Looking for a family dental clinic in Saskatoon?
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-[var(--color-text-muted)] leading-relaxed">
        Wildwood Dental Clinic serves patients of all ages in Saskatoon, SK. We would be happy to welcome your family.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="/book" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">
          Book an Appointment
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"/></svg>
        </a>
        <a href="/new-patients" class="btn btn-outline btn-lg">
          New Patient Info
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
